rows.label: tlk006501_02_msg0001
rows.name:
It's not like I've
forgiven those brats.

rows.label: tlk006501_02_msg0002
rows.name:
They might look like they're
working hard, but they're the
ones who stole from me, you know?

rows.label: tlk006501_02_msg0003
rows.name:
No matter if your hometown is
gone and you're just trying to
survive, stealing is wrong.

rows.label: tlk006501_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know what they'll pull next.
I can't let my guard down yet.
